isbnlookup.sh
Bash-Script for organizing of pdf ebooks

isbn_lookup uses pdftotext to extract the book ISBN number.
Then amazon.com is queried, using the isbn number, to get the 
title of the book. The Script builds a filesystem-clean filename
containing the booktitle and isbn number.

Suggestions, patches/forks welcome.

gitHub Repository: http://github.com/yvesf/isbnlookup.sh
